caption:
The most successful people I've met:

1. Harvest the Building from the Architect
2. Always crouch desperately before the orifice of the Chef for the Gnocchi to ooze forth
3. Promote Fermentation that make Beer
4. Empower Plants to make Fruit
5. Cherish the Smoke that come out of Fire
6. Support Plants to grow the Sugar community
